 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# CC API 0.1.0a1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import lettertask as lt\n",
    "import patches\n",
    "import predicode as pc\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.optim as optim\n",
    "from tqdm import tqdm\n",
    "import lazytools_sflippl as lazytools\n",
    "import plotnine as gg\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import torch"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_1 = lt.data.CompositionalBinaryModel(samples=100).to_array().reshape(1, 100, 100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_2 = pc.datasets.Cifar10().data.transpose(0, 3, 1, 2)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ds_1 = patches.data.ContrastiveDataset(data_1, contrast_type='both', prediction_range=5)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ds_2 = patches.data.ContrastiveDataset(data_2, contrast_type='samples')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "torch.Size([10, 3, 32, 32])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ds_2[0].shape"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Contrastive coder"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "encoder = nn.Linear(100, 1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "predictor = nn.Linear(1, 5)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cc = patches.networks.ContrastiveCoder(encoder, predictor)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "criterion = patches.losses.ContrastiveLoss(criterion=nn.MSELoss())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor(2.3047, grad_fn=<NegBackward>)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 11,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "criterion(**cc(ds_1[0]))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Test"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We translate chapter 10."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cbm = lt.data.CompositionalBinaryModel(\n",
    "    width=[50, 10, 20, 40, 100, 40],\n",
    "    change_probability=[0.05, 0.5, 0.2, 0.5, 0.1, 0.2],\n",
    "    samples=100000,\n",
    "    seed=None\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "dataset = patches.data.ContrastiveDataset(cbm.to_array().reshape(1, 100000, 260),\n",
    "                                          contrast_type='both',\n",
    "                                          prediction_range=5)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cc = patches.networks.ContrastiveCoder(nn.Linear(260, 2), nn.Linear(2, 10))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "criterion = patches.losses.ContrastiveLoss(criterion=patches.losses.BilinearLoss())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "tensor(2.3026, grad_fn=<NegBackward>)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "criterion(**cc(dataset[0]))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ideal_1 = np.array([1]*50+[0]*(10+20+40+100+40))/np.sqrt(50)\n",
    "ideal_2 = np.array([0]*(50+10+20+40)+[1]*100+[0]*40)/np.sqrt(100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 23,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "optimizer = optim.Adam(cc.parameters(), lr=1e-1)\n",
    "angle_1 = []\n",
    "angle_2 = []\n",
    "loss_traj = []\n",
    "running_loss = 0\n",
    "n_epochs = 1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 31,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "torch.Size([10, 6, 260])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 31,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "data.shape"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 24,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "100%|██████████| 99995/99995 [02:21<00:00, 707.06it/s]\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "with tqdm(total=n_epochs*len(dataset)) as pbar:\n",
    "    for epoch in range(n_epochs):\n",
    "        running_loss = 0\n",
    "        for i in range(len(dataset)):\n",
    "            data = dataset[i]\n",
    "            if i % 10 == 0:\n",
    "                est = list(cc.parameters())[0].detach().numpy()\n",
    "                angle_1.append(np.matmul(ideal_1, est[0,:].T)/np.sqrt(np.matmul(est[0,:], est[0,:].T)) +\n",
    "                               np.matmul(ideal_1, est[1,:].T)/np.sqrt(np.matmul(est[1,:], est[1,:].T)))\n",
    "                angle_2.append(np.matmul(ideal_2, est[0,:].T)/np.sqrt(np.matmul(est[0,:], est[0,:].T)) +\n",
    "                               np.matmul(ideal_2, est[1,:].T)/np.sqrt(np.matmul(est[1,:], est[1,:].T)))\n",
    "            optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "            code = cc(data)\n",
    "            loss = criterion(**code)\n",
    "            loss.backward()\n",
    "            optimizer.step()\n",
    "            running_loss += loss\n",
    "            if i % 500 == 499:\n",
    "                loss_traj.append(running_loss.detach().numpy()/500)\n",
    "                running_loss = 0\n",
    "            pbar.update(1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 25,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [

      ]

     "execution_count": 25,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "loss_df = lazytools.array_to_dataframe(np.array(loss_traj))\\\n",
    "                   .rename(columns={'dim0': 'steps', 'array': 'loss'})\n",
    "(gg.ggplot(loss_df, gg.aes(x='steps', y='loss')) +\n",
    "    gg.geom_line())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 26,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [

     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "angle_1_df = lazytools.array_to_dataframe(np.array(angle_1))\\\n",
    "                      .rename(columns={'dim0': 'steps', 'array': 'angle'})\n",
    "angle_1_df['latent_dim'] = np.array('1')\n",
    "angle_2_df = lazytools.array_to_dataframe(np.array(angle_2))\\\n",
    "                      .rename(columns={'dim0': 'steps', 'array': 'angle'})\n",
    "angle_2_df['latent_dim'] = np.array('2')\n",
    "angle_df = pd.concat([angle_1_df, angle_2_df])\n",
    "(gg.ggplot(angle_df, gg.aes(x='steps', y='angle')) +\n",
    "    gg.geom_line() + \n",
    "    gg.facet_wrap('latent_dim'))"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},

    "Overall, this run included three contrastive epochs, which essentially corresponds to thirty conventional epochs? However, the algorithm has found a good minimum after a fraction of this time!"
